    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "those unusual readings you mentioned... are we talking about sensor glitches or actual interference patterns? if there was a structure there, there would have to be some kind of electromagnetic signature or shadow anomaly that doesn't match the lunar terrain. specifically, look at the telemetry from the 1969 descent—was there any signal dropout or sudden course corrections that weren't explained in the official debriefs?",
